1
00:00:30,570 --> 00:00:35,920
[The Duel of Hearts]

2
00:00:34,140 --> 00:00:35,920
[Episode 6]

3
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:40,960
[Taiji Palace]

4
00:00:43,820 --> 00:00:46,900
[The Aeom Sutra]

5
00:00:47,120 --> 00:00:51,320
[Taiji Palace]

6
00:00:51,460 --> 00:00:52,340
Pick it up!

7
00:00:53,500 --> 00:00:55,030
Hurry up!

8
00:00:55,220 --> 00:00:56,400
Greetings, Supreme General.

9
00:00:59,050 --> 00:00:59,890
Brother.

10
00:01:00,240 --> 00:01:01,230
Save me!

11
00:01:07,070 --> 00:01:08,830
I'm Shao.

12
00:01:12,460 --> 00:01:15,300
I... I'm Shao.

13
00:01:22,289 --> 00:01:23,710
[The Aeom Sutra]

14
00:01:25,860 --> 00:01:27,140
Noble Consort Wen is being foolish.

15
00:01:27,900 --> 00:01:28,700
Guards!

16
00:01:29,210 --> 00:01:30,370
Make her come to her senses.

17
00:01:30,710 --> 00:01:31,370
Yes.

18
00:01:48,370 --> 00:01:49,729
Minister Wen still won't give up？

19
00:01:49,750 --> 00:01:51,060
Your Majesty, you have taken the throne.

20
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:53,360
If I die with my sister,

21
00:01:53,530 --> 00:01:56,009
wouldn’t that perfectly fulfill 
Your Majesty’s grand ambitions?

22
00:01:56,870 --> 00:01:57,560
Your Majesty.

23
00:01:59,479 --> 00:02:01,320
Behave yourself.

24
00:02:04,700 --> 00:02:05,290
Your Majesty.

25
00:02:05,770 --> 00:02:06,590
I found the truth.

26
00:02:06,730 --> 00:02:08,650
This was found at the place 
where the Empress Dowager fainted.

27
00:02:11,140 --> 00:02:12,580
I also heard that

28
00:02:12,750 --> 00:02:14,770
a masked woman dressed strangely

29
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:16,710
has been living at the place

30
00:02:16,850 --> 00:02:18,210
where the Empress Dowager 
and Noble Consort Wen fainted.

31
00:02:19,210 --> 00:02:19,890
By the way,

32
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:22,820
she seemed to have
 a bird tattoo on her neck.

33
00:02:24,290 --> 00:02:26,480
A'Man? Could she be A'Man?

34
00:02:27,610 --> 00:02:29,030
What else was found at the scene?

35
00:02:30,140 --> 00:02:30,900
The altar table;

36
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:32,579
candlesticks and river lanterns.

37
00:02:32,930 --> 00:02:34,590
As if some kind of formation
 was being performed.

38
00:02:35,860 --> 00:02:37,110
The year of Gengwu.

39
00:02:37,470 --> 00:02:38,270
The month of Shen.

40
00:02:39,890 --> 00:02:40,700
The formation.

41
00:02:41,650 --> 00:02:42,920
I'll take my leave.

42
00:02:54,630 --> 00:02:55,650
Wen Zhao.

43
00:02:57,170 --> 00:02:59,410
Why have you become so weird lately?

44
00:03:00,980 --> 00:03:03,130
Don't play hard to get.

45
00:03:08,060 --> 00:03:09,200
Didn't you

46
00:03:10,490 --> 00:03:11,860
used to long for

47
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:13,030
♫Time flies like light
 and shines in your hands♫

48
00:03:13,190 --> 00:03:15,230
such closeness with me?

49
00:03:14,340 --> 00:03:16,140
♫Look at the blooming flowers♫

50
00:03:16,770 --> 00:03:18,500
I'm just tired.

51
00:03:17,290 --> 00:03:19,740
♫Day after day, how can I mention love?♫

52
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:20,070
I don't mean anything else.

53
00:03:21,230 --> 00:03:22,990
♫Who panicked?♫

54
00:03:24,630 --> 00:03:25,650
♫Your thoughts are hard to remember♫

55
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:30,250
♫I can't write anything in a rush♫

56
00:03:31,620 --> 00:03:35,630
♫If you get the wrong idea, time will fade♫

57
00:03:34,730 --> 00:03:37,140
Have I not regained my memory yet?

58
00:03:37,170 --> 00:03:38,650
If Empress Dowager were here,

59
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:40,990
♫Flowers blooming and withering, 
I have no choice♫

60
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:41,470
she would surely not wish
 for Your Majesty to become like this.

61
00:03:42,150 --> 00:03:43,150
I'm not Wen Zhao.

62
00:03:42,470 --> 00:03:44,579
♫No matter what fate it is,
 love and hate will last for years♫

63
00:03:43,180 --> 00:03:44,470
I'm not Wen Zhao.

64
00:03:45,900 --> 00:03:48,170
♫The sea of stars in your eyes. 
The love I want in my life♫

65
00:03:46,170 --> 00:03:46,650
Your Majesty.

66
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,760
Who asked her to kneel here?

67
00:03:49,110 --> 00:03:51,030
Didn't you ask her to kneel?

68
00:03:49,420 --> 00:03:51,600
♫Time flies, yet I never forget♫

69
00:03:51,060 --> 00:03:51,800
Shao.

70
00:03:52,980 --> 00:03:55,000
♫In this life, 
I only want to keep you in heart♫

71
00:03:56,500 --> 00:03:58,730
♫But everything in the world 
can't be fulfilled♫

72
00:03:57,390 --> 00:03:58,360
Call the imperial physician!

73
00:03:59,120 --> 00:03:59,930
Yes.

74
00:04:00,290 --> 00:04:05,210
♫Countless lovers by the sea 
beg for destiny in the next life♫

75
00:04:02,180 --> 00:04:03,840
[Hehuan Palace]

76
00:04:07,230 --> 00:04:09,520
♫I'd rather endure this long calamity♫

77
00:04:07,580 --> 00:04:09,140
I'm such a fool.

78
00:04:09,470 --> 00:04:11,620
I couldn't recognize you with so many flaws.

79
00:04:10,550 --> 00:04:12,950
♫But the word love in this life 
is destined to be unsolvable♫

80
00:04:11,980 --> 00:04:13,870
I never expected you 
to come up with something

81
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:19,529
♫You bring endless snow to fall in my heart♫

82
00:04:14,300 --> 00:04:16,519
as drastic as body-swapping 
just to leave me.

83
00:04:25,450 --> 00:04:26,250
Shao.

84
00:04:27,020 --> 00:04:29,190
I won't let you leave this time.

85
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:39,400
Empress Dowager.

86
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,340
His Majesty publicly punished Noble Consort Wen

87
00:04:41,370 --> 00:04:42,730
for the fake pregnancy;

88
00:04:43,080 --> 00:04:45,250
and made her recite sutras
 to pray for your blessings.

89
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:53,920
A'Bu.

90
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:55,120
Go get some ice.

91
00:04:55,350 --> 00:04:56,050
Yes.

92
00:05:06,430 --> 00:05:07,280
- Your Majesty.
- You're awake.

93
00:05:10,960 --> 00:05:12,690
I can't let Shao realize that

94
00:05:12,880 --> 00:05:15,160
I know she has become Wen Zhao.

95
00:05:15,740 --> 00:05:17,780
Or else she will keep me at arm's length.

96
00:05:18,520 --> 00:05:20,140
Why am I here?

97
00:05:21,710 --> 00:05:23,370
I'll take my leave now.

98
00:05:24,380 --> 00:05:25,180
Don't move.

99
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:32,720
Your Majesty.

100
00:05:33,300 --> 00:05:34,850
I'll take my leave.

101
00:05:37,030 --> 00:05:38,800
You are my darling.

102
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:41,010
I'll send you back.

103
00:05:43,630 --> 00:05:44,960
I can't let her realize that

104
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,200
I know the truth.

105
00:05:52,690 --> 00:05:55,150
[Hehuan Palace]

106
00:06:04,430 --> 00:06:05,310
Are you

107
00:06:05,830 --> 00:06:06,790
blaming me?

108
00:06:08,030 --> 00:06:09,350
I dare not.

109
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:10,520
You dare not?

110
00:06:12,110 --> 00:06:13,180
That means you are blaming me.

111
00:06:14,730 --> 00:06:15,500
No.

112
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,300
If not,

113
00:06:19,660 --> 00:06:21,010
then,

114
00:06:21,510 --> 00:06:23,230
I shall sleep in your palace

115
00:06:23,610 --> 00:06:24,250
tonight.

116
00:06:28,110 --> 00:06:29,910
What if I say yes?

117
00:06:32,150 --> 00:06:33,810
Then I have to stay

118
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:35,760
to apologize to you

119
00:06:36,010 --> 00:06:37,190
and make you happy.

120
00:06:38,300 --> 00:06:40,780
Your Majesty, 
if you really want me to be happy,

121
00:06:41,180 --> 00:06:43,250
can you do me a favor?

122
00:06:45,500 --> 00:06:46,400
Say it.

123
00:06:48,260 --> 00:06:50,040
I want to be alone.

124
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:54,580
Can’t I be at peace here?

125
00:07:09,940 --> 00:07:10,740
That's...

126
00:07:13,860 --> 00:07:15,260
That's the secret room

127
00:07:15,370 --> 00:07:17,400
where you kept poison and hidden weapons.

128
00:07:24,590 --> 00:07:25,390
Wen Zhao.

129
00:07:26,290 --> 00:07:29,270
How many hidden weapons 
have you hidden in Hehuan Palace?

130
00:07:29,420 --> 00:07:32,280
Do you intend to kill me?

131
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:35,909
I dare not.

132
00:07:36,100 --> 00:07:37,510
After I fainted,

133
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:38,280
I...

134
00:07:38,280 --> 00:07:40,240
Enough. Stop making excuses.

135
00:07:40,980 --> 00:07:42,110
From now on,

136
00:07:42,330 --> 00:07:43,750
you'll move to Chengqian Palace.

137
00:07:43,980 --> 00:07:44,840
When you've cleared up

138
00:07:44,840 --> 00:07:46,440
the memories from before,

139
00:07:46,909 --> 00:07:48,190
that's when you can move back.

140
00:07:51,390 --> 00:07:53,110
Yes, Your Majesty.

141
00:07:53,290 --> 00:07:57,580
[Chengqian Palace]

142
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:01,060
It's too dangerous!

143
00:08:03,220 --> 00:08:04,500
It's really too dangerous!

144
00:08:05,410 --> 00:08:06,150
See.

145
00:08:06,330 --> 00:08:08,290
[Hall] [Traps] [Bed]

146
00:08:06,510 --> 00:08:07,160
Here, and here.

147
00:08:07,250 --> 00:08:09,360
With so many traps, 
you can't even remember them yourself.

148
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,020
Let me tell you.

149
00:08:14,490 --> 00:08:16,000
You will stay in my palace.

150
00:08:16,020 --> 00:08:17,120
It’s the safest place.

151
00:08:17,510 --> 00:08:19,460
Once you’re familiar with everything,

152
00:08:20,020 --> 00:08:21,540
I’ll naturally let you go.

153
00:08:26,530 --> 00:08:27,770
I heard that

154
00:08:27,830 --> 00:08:29,020
you haven't had a meal all day?

155
00:08:29,130 --> 00:08:29,860
Sit.

156
00:08:36,990 --> 00:08:38,990
Probably because of the intense heat lately;

157
00:08:39,620 --> 00:08:42,299
I have no appetite.

158
00:08:47,430 --> 00:08:48,810
Try this.

159
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:51,210
Your Majesty, I'll do it myself.

160
00:08:54,010 --> 00:08:54,610
Open your mouth.

161
00:09:10,490 --> 00:09:11,150
Enough.

162
00:09:11,460 --> 00:09:12,190
Do it yourself.

163
00:09:21,420 --> 00:09:23,430
Isn't this the soup I taught him to make?

164
00:09:24,010 --> 00:09:24,790
I didn't expect that

165
00:09:25,530 --> 00:09:27,640
he would use it to please Wen Zhao.

166
00:09:28,520 --> 00:09:30,280
[Chengqian Palace]

167
00:09:30,670 --> 00:09:32,160
Your Majesty, 
Do you want me to serve in bed?

168
00:09:32,630 --> 00:09:33,150
Exactly.
